1-css: to make the card turn: div{transition: transform 1s;}
then hover {transform:rotateY(180deg)}
https://www.w3schools.com/css/tryit.asp?filename=trycss3_transition_transform
https://www.w3schools.com/cssref/css3_pr_transform-origin.php#gsc.tab=0

2-The difference between FlaskForm and <form>
https://github.com/alaaibr25/StudiesForMe.git

3- use render_temp() to get data from another function,
and you can loop through it.

@app.route('/add', methods=['POST', 'GET'])
def add_page():
    add_form = AddForm()
    if add_form.validate_on_submit():
        results = response['results']
        return render_template('select.html', data=results)
    return render_template('add.html', form=add_form)

@app.route('/select', methods=['POST', 'GET'])
def select_movie():
    return render_template('select.html')

